// In this guide you will find a list of frequently performed tasks and the corresponding linux code to complete them...

1. How to determine the path of an installed program?

> which [name of app]

For instance

> which matchbox-keyboard
> which leafpad

2. How to create text files from terminal?

> sudo nano

Recall that "sudo" grants permission from the administrator or the super user. Hence, "nano" is the real text editor command...
